ss=title> Re: Armor self-buffs ... mana regeneration?</span><hr size=1> Blessed armour of the Risen (unlike Flowing Thought I or II items) makes a noticable difference in mana regeneration, especially when you don't have C2 or a bard at hand.<br>
<br>
Imho it was about time that Verant added a means for clerics to increase their mana regeneration, pre SoL we were the only caster class (except mages) without this ability.<br>
