Increase Total Hit Points from 202 (L34) to 225 (L42)<br>
Increase Armor Class (AC) by 15 (L34)<br>
Increase Current Hitpoints from 202 (L34) to 225 (L42)<br>
<br>
Armor of the Faithful<br>
Increase Total Hit Points from 252 (L49) to 275 (L57)<br>
Increase Armor Class (AC) by 23 (L49)<br>
Increase Current Hitpoints from 252 (L49) to 275 (L57)<br>
<br>
Blessed Armor of the Risen<br>
Increase Total Hit Points from 294 (L58) to 300 (L60)<br>
Increase Armor Class (AC) by 30 (L58)<br>
Increase Current Hitpoints from 294 (L58) to 300 (L60)<br>
Increase Mana by 6 (L58)<br>
<br>
From the SDat.  And I wholeheartedly agree Xanthor. <p><TABLE BORDER="0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
